# Game Economy – Mobile Systems

## Goals
- Design balanced in-game currency, item economy, and progression rewards.
- Prevent exploits; ensure server authority for currency changes.
- Integrate with IAP, ads, and live events for monetization.

## Core Concepts
- Currencies: soft/hard currencies, energy, premium tokens.
- Balance: pacing curves, inflation control, expenditure sinks.
- Inventory lifecycle: acquisition, consumption, upgrades, disposals.

## Data Model
- CurrencyBalance(user_id, currency_type, amount)
- TransactionLog(id, user_id, amount, type, source, created_at)
- ItemDefinitions(id, name, price, rarity, currency_type)

## Rules & Invariants
- All wallet changes validated server-side.
- Atomic transactions for multi-step purchases.
- Idempotent operations for retries.

## Monetization Hooks
- IAP purchases, time-limited offers, bundles.
- Ad-based rewards and daily login bonuses.

## Performance & Security
- Cache visible balances with short TTLs; invalidate on changes.
- Harden cryptographic validation for purchases.

