# Cocos2d-JS Performance (3.x)

## Core Principles
- Draw call minimization through atlas batching.
- Memory pooling and reuse in hot paths.
- Efficient asset loading and early binding.

## Techniques
- Group sprites by atlas to maximize batching.
- Avoid per-frame allocations in update loops.
- Use bitmap fonts and spritesheets to reduce texture changes.

